                "invention-title": [
                    "Denitration method for tail gas generated after hydrogen combustion",
                    "一种氢气燃烧后尾气脱硝方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention is applicable to the technical field of denitration, and provides a method for denitration of tail gas after hydrogen combustion, which comprises the following steps: adsorbing NOx in the waste gas obtained after hydrogen combustion by using an adsorbent; nOx reacts with water in the waste gas to generate nitric acid and release NO; nOx reacts with water in the waste gas to release NO, and NO in the tail gas reacts with oxygen to generate NO2; nO2 is adsorbed by the adsorbent; carrying out desorption treatment on the saturated adsorbent and then releasing NO2; nO2 released by the adsorbent reacts with water to generate nitric acid. According to the tail gas denitration method after hydrogen combustion provided by the embodiment of the invention, water in the waste gas obtained after hydrogen combustion reacts with NOx, nitric acid is successfully prepared while denitration is performed, and the economic benefit is favorably improved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本申请适用于脱硝技术领域，提供了一种氢气燃烧后尾气脱硝方法，包括：利用吸附剂吸附氢气燃烧后所得废气中的NOx；NOx与废气中的水反应生成硝酸并放出NO；NOx与废气中的水反应放出的NO和尾气中的NO，均与氧反应生成NO2；NO2被所述吸附剂吸附；达到饱和的吸附剂经脱附处理后放出NO2；吸附剂放出的NO2与水反应生成硝酸。本申请实施例提供的氢气燃烧后尾气脱硝方法，将氢气燃烧后所得废气中的水和NOx反应，在脱硝的同时成功制取硝酸，有利于提高经济效益。"
                }
            ]
